Alembic migrations for the GeoSWMM Gateway.

This directory is bootstrapped from the async template. The first real
migration (users + refresh_tokens) is added in Phase 2 by the db-engineer
sub-agent. Until then `alembic upgrade head` is a no-op.

Common commands (run inside the `app` container):

    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add foo"
    alembic upgrade head
    alembic downgrade -1

Always inspect the autogenerated diff before committing — Alembic mis-detects
index changes occasionally.
